{"word":"G3979 - πεζῇ - pezēi - ped-zay' - A- foot","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πεζῇ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pezēi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ped-zay'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">A- foot</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கால்நடையாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. on foot (as opposed to riding)"},{"paragraph":"2. by land (as opposed to going by sea)"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Dative feminine of a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4228 - πούς - poús - pooce/4228\">G4228</a> (as adverb); <i>foot wise</i>, that is, by <i>walking:</i> - a- (on) foot.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}